<section class="border-t border-base-200 dark:border-base-700 pt-10 pb-12">
    <h2 class="font-display text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-base-400 dark:text-base-500 mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <dl class="space-y-5 max-w-2xl">
        <div>
            <dt class="font-display font-medium text-base-700 dark:text-base-300 text-sm">Are these docs finished?</dt>
            <dd class="text-sm text-base-500 dark:text-base-500 mt-0.5">No.</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
            <dt class="font-display font-medium text-base-700 dark:text-base-300 text-sm">Is this app bug-free and ready for production?</dt>
            <dd class="text-sm text-base-500 dark:text-base-500 mt-0.5">Not even close.</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
            <dt class="font-display font-medium text-base-700 dark:text-base-300 text-sm">Is there a migration tool from my favorite documentation tool?</dt>
            <dd class="text-sm text-base-500 dark:text-base-500 mt-0.5">No.</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
            <dt class="font-display font-medium text-base-700 dark:text-base-300 text-sm">Is this an appropriate tool for my non-.NET project?</dt>
            <dd class="text-sm text-base-500 dark:text-base-500 mt-0.5">Probably not, but knock yourself out.</dd>
        </div>
        <div>
            <dt class="font-display font-medium text-base-700 dark:text-base-300 text-sm">Can I submit a pull request?</dt>
            <dd class="text-sm text-base-500 dark:text-base-500 mt-0.5">
                Yeah, but hop on the <a href="https://github.com/phil-scott-78/penn/discussions" class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">GitHub discussions</a> first before getting too far ahead of yourself.
            </dd>
        </div>
        <div>
            <dt class="font-display font-medium text-base-700 dark:text-base-300 text-sm">There's a missing feature my company critically needs — it's costing us $1000 a day!</dt>
            <dd class="text-sm text-base-500 dark:text-base-500 mt-0.5">I'll add it for $999 a day.</dd>
        </div>
    </dl>
</section>
